00:05:22.345 --> 00:05:23.806
The average fixed costs,

00:05:23.806 --> 00:05:25.092
or actually the marginal costs,

00:05:25.092 --> 00:05:26.084
the average variable costs

00:05:26.084 --> 00:05:27.250
