00:05:44.487 --> 00:05:46.542
those first oranges that we bought

00:05:46.542 --> 00:05:47.289
were expensive.

00:05:47.289 --> 00:05:48.924
We weren't a major producer,

00:05:48.924 --> 00:05:49.793
but incrementally,

00:05:49.793 --> 00:05:53.009
incrementally, as we
produce those next oranges,

00:05:53.009 --> 00:05:55.298
so as we go from 1,000 oranges,

00:05:55.298 --> 00:05:58.568
as we go from the oranges
needed for 1,000 gallons

00:05:58.568 --> 00:06:00.896
