00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:09.420
As we get even more,

00:06:09.420 --> 00:06:11.365
as we go to 3,000
gallons worth of oranges,

00:06:11.365 --> 00:06:14.523
those incremental oranges
get even cheaper for us.

00:06:14.523 --> 00:06:15.991
Then we have to go and buy oranges

00:06:15.991 --> 00:06:17.236
from the outside,

00:06:17.236 --> 00:06:19.868
so those incremental
oranges get more and more

00:06:19.868 --> 00:06:22.074
